<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="SnappyX: America's trusted 24/7 water damage restoration company serving all 50 states. Emergency response, IICRC-certified technicians, and insurance assistance.">
  <title>SnappyX | 24/7 Nationwide Water Damage Restoration Company</title>
  
  <!-- Fonts -->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  
  <!-- Tailwind -->
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            'trust-blue': '#0056b3',
            'emergency-red': '#d9534f',
          },
          fontFamily: {
            'inter': ['Inter', 'sans-serif'],
          }
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
  
  <!-- AlpineJS for interactivity (optional) -->
  <script defer src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/alpinejs@3.x.x/dist/cdn.min.js"></script>
  
  <style>
    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }
    .stats-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .stats-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
    details > summary {
      list-style: none;
    }
    details > summary::-webkit-details-marker {
      display: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body class="font-inter text-gray-800 bg-white">
  <!-- HEADER -->
  <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-white shadow-md">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-4">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
        <!-- Logo -->
        <div class="flex items-center">
          <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-trust-blue">SnappyX</h1>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Navigation -->
        <nav class="hidden md:flex items-center space-x-8">
          <a href="#" class="font-medium hover:text-trust-blue transition">Home</a>
          <a href="#" class="font-medium hover:text-trust-blue transition">About</a>
          <a href="#" class="font-medium hover:text-trust-blue transition">Services</a>
          <a href="#" class="font-medium hover:text-trust-blue transition">Contact</a>
          <a href="tel:5550123456" class="bg-emergency-red text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-red-600 transition">
            Call Now: (555) 012-3456
          </a>
        </nav>
        
        <!-- Mobile menu button -->
        <button class="md:hidden" @click="open = !open" x-data="{ open: false }">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path x-show="!open" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16"></path>
            <path x-show="open" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
          </svg>
        </button>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Mobile Navigation -->
      <div class="md:hidden mt-4" x-show="open" x-transition>
        <div class="flex flex-col space-y-4">
          <a href="#" class="font-medium py-2">Home</a>
          <a href="#" class="font-medium py-2">About</a>
          <a href="#" class="font-medium py-2">Services</a>
          <a href="#" class="font-medium py-2">Contact</a>
          <a href="tel:5550123456" class="bg-emergency-red text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold text-center">
            Call Now: (555) 012-3456
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-trust-blue to-blue-800 text-white py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">24/7 Water Damage Restoration Company Serving All 50 States</h1>
          
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">
            When water damage strikes, every minute counts. SnappyX provides nationwide emergency water damage restoration services with local, licensed teams ready to respond 24/7. Our certified technicians utilize advanced extraction and drying technology to mitigate damage and restore your property. We serve residential and commercial clients across America, maintaining consistent quality standards and rapid response times regardless of location. Our comprehensive approach includes water extraction, structural drying, mold prevention, and insurance claim assistance‚Äîall backed by IICRC certification and extensive industry experience.
          </p>
          
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a href="tel:5550123456" class="bg-emergency-red hover:bg-red-600 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg text-center text-lg transition duration-300">
              Get Help Now
            </a>
            <a href="#services" class="bg-white text-trust-blue hover:bg-gray-100 font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg text-center text-lg transition duration-300">
              Our Services
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CORE SERVICES GRID -->
    <section id="services" class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-900">Professional Water Damage Restoration Services</h2>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Water Damage Restoration -->
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-trust-blue text-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-2xl">üíß</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Water Damage Restoration</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Comprehensive restoration services for all water damage scenarios. Our systematic approach includes assessment, water extraction, drying, and restoration to pre-loss conditions using industry-leading equipment and proven techniques.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Emergency Water Removal -->
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emergency-red text-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-2xl">üö®</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Emergency Water Removal</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Immediate response for water extraction to prevent secondary damage. Our teams arrive with powerful truck-mounted extraction units and submersible pumps to remove standing water quickly and efficiently.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Flood Cleanup -->
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-trust-blue text-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-2xl">üåä</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Flood Cleanup</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Specialized cleanup services for flood-affected properties. We handle contaminated water situations with appropriate safety protocols, thorough cleaning, and antimicrobial treatments to ensure a healthy environment.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Structural Drying -->
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-trust-blue text-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-2xl">üèóÔ∏è</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Structural Drying</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Advanced drying techniques for walls, floors, and building materials. Using moisture mapping technology and industrial dehumidifiers, we achieve proper drying to prevent warping, swelling, and mold growth.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Mold Mitigation -->
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-trust-blue text-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-2xl">ü¶†</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Mold Mitigation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Professional mold remediation following IICRC S520 standards. We contain affected areas, remove contaminated materials safely, clean surfaces with EPA-approved solutions, and apply preventive treatments.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TRUST & EEAT BLOCK -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-trust-blue text-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Why Property Owners Nationwide Trust SnappyX</h2>
          
          <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
            <!-- Trust Points -->
            <div>
              <ul class="space-y-4">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-emergency-red text-2xl mr-3">‚úì</span>
                  <span class="text-lg"><strong>Licensed & Insured:</strong> Fully licensed water damage restoration company with comprehensive liability insurance and workers' compensation coverage.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-emergency-red text-2xl mr-3">‚úì</span>
                  <span class="text-lg"><strong>IICRC-Certified Technicians:</strong> All restoration specialists hold current Institute of Inspection, Cleaning and Restoration Certification credentials.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-emergency-red text-2xl mr-3">‚úì</span>
                  <span class="text-lg"><strong>Insurance Claim Assistance:</strong> We work directly with all major insurance providers and help document damages for claim processing.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-emergency-red text-2xl mr-3">‚úì</span>
                  <span class="text-lg"><strong>24/7/365 Response:</strong> Our emergency dispatch center operates around the clock, including holidays, with local teams nationwide.</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Stats -->
            <div class="bg-white text-gray-900 p-8 rounded-xl">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Our National Impact</h3>
              <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="text-center">
                  <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-trust-blue mb-2">15+</div>
                  <div class="text-gray-600">Years in Business</div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                  <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-trust-blue mb-2">50K+</div>
                  <div class="text-gray-600">Jobs Handled</div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                  <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-trust-blue mb-2">60</div>
                  <div class="text-gray-600">Min Avg Response</div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                  <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-trust-blue mb-2">50</div>
                  <div class="text-gray-600">States Served</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- MICRO "WHO WE ARE" -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">About SnappyX Restoration</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">
            SnappyX is a legally registered national restoration corporation headquartered in the United States. Our brand entity maintains strict operational standards across all 50 states, ensuring consistent quality and professional service delivery. Every technician undergoes rigorous background checks, continuous training, and must maintain active certifications. We operate as a unified national brand with localized service delivery teams, allowing us to provide rapid emergency response while maintaining corporate accountability and standardized service protocols.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
            Our corporate structure enables us to maintain consistent pricing, warranty coverage, and quality assurance nationwide while complying with all state and local regulations. We invest in ongoing technician education, equipment upgrades, and industry research to remain at the forefront of restoration technology and methodology.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- STATES WE SERVE -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">States We Serve</h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-4 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <!-- 24 popular states -->
          {['Texas', 'Florida', 'California', 'New York', 'Ohio', 'Pennsylvania', 'Illinois', 'Georgia', 'North Carolina', 'Michigan', 'New Jersey', 'Virginia', 'Washington', 'Arizona', 'Tennessee', 'Massachusetts', 'Indiana', 'Missouri', 'Maryland', 'Wisconsin', 'Colorado', 'Minnesota', 'South Carolina', 'Alabama'].map(state => (
            <a 
              href={`/services/${state.toLowerCase().replace(' ', '-')}`} 
              class="bg-white hover:bg-trust-blue hover:text-white text-center py-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition duration-300 font-medium"
            >
              {state}
            </a>
          ))}
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-center mt-8 text-gray-600">
          Plus all other U.S. states and territories. We maintain licensed restoration teams nationwide.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- EMERGENCY CTA -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-emergency-red text-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Call Now for Immediate Water Damage Help</h2>
        <p class="text-xl mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Don't wait‚Äîwater damage worsens quickly. Our emergency dispatch connects you to local certified technicians.
        </p>
        <a href="tel:5550123456" class="inline-block bg-white text-emergency-red hover:bg-gray-100 text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold py-6 px-12 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl transition duration-300">
          (555) 012-3456
        </a>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg">Available 24 hours, 7 days a week, including holidays</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- MINI FAQ -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
          <details class="border rounded-lg p-4 hover:shadow-md transition">
            <summary class="font-bold text-lg cursor-pointer flex justify-between items-center">
              What is your average emergency response time?
              <span class="text-trust-blue text-2xl">+</span>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-gray-700 pt-3 border-t">
              Our national average emergency response time is 60 minutes or less. When you call our emergency hotline, we immediately dispatch the nearest available certified team from our nationwide network. Response times vary by location and weather conditions, but we maintain strategically positioned teams to ensure rapid service across all 50 states.
            </p>
          </details>

          <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
          <details class="border rounded-lg p-4 hover:shadow-md transition">
            <summary class="font-bold text-lg cursor-pointer flex justify-between items-center">
              Do you work directly with insurance companies?
              <span class="text-trust-blue text-2xl">+</span>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-gray-700 pt-3 border-t">
              Yes, we work directly with all major insurance providers. Our team assists with the entire claims process, including detailed documentation, moisture mapping, and proper paperwork. We follow insurance industry standards and can often bill your insurance company directly, minimizing your out-of-pocket expenses and simplifying the restoration process.
            </p>
          </details>

          <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
          <details class="border rounded-lg p-4 hover:shadow-md transition">
            <summary class="font-bold text-lg cursor-pointer flex justify-between items-center">
              What types of water damage do you handle?
              <span class="text-trust-blue text-2xl">+</span>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-gray-700 pt-3 border-t">
              We handle all categories of water damage: Category 1 (clean water from supply lines), Category 2 (gray water with some contamination), and Category 3 (black water with severe contamination). Our services address flooding, burst pipes, sewage backups, appliance leaks, storm damage, and foundation water intrusion. All contaminated water situations are handled with appropriate safety protocols and equipment.
            </p>
          </details>

          <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
          <details class="border rounded-lg p-4 hover:shadow-md transition">
            <summary class="font-bold text-lg cursor-pointer flex justify-between items-center">
              Are your technicians certified and background-checked?
              <span class="text-trust-blue text-2xl">+</span>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-gray-700 pt-3 border-t">
              Absolutely. Every SnappyX technician holds current IICRC (Institute of Inspection, Cleaning and Restoration Certification) credentials. All team members undergo comprehensive background checks, drug screening, and continuous training. We maintain strict hiring standards and invest in ongoing education to ensure our teams are updated on the latest restoration techniques and safety protocols.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
